    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterpiece of high-revving mechanical purity. This example features the iconic S54 inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously overhauled for optimal cam timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery to the rear wheels. Structural integrity is guaranteed with a reinforced rear subframe, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with zero bushing deflection. With documented rod bearing replacement and a recent valve adjustment, this specimen offers a visceral, analog experience in flawless aesthetic and mechanical order.",
