    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or door dings to be found. Every panel alignment is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin remains in a showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear, creasing, or fading, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. The carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since the first mile, and every electronic component, button, and digital display functions with out-of-the-box precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive, chronological binder of service records included in the sale. Always garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, the undercarriage is as pristine as the bodywork. This is, without question, the finest example available on the market for a discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
